1
00:00:00,208 --> 00:00:02,333
They used to call it the lecture hall

2
00:00:03,750 --> 00:00:07,250
When they released the prisoner, they released him

3
00:00:07,791 --> 00:00:12,208
They told him, The judge sentenced you to 15 days or a month

4
00:00:12,541 --> 00:00:16,000
You have to come and check in, every day you attend the hall

5
00:00:16,708 --> 00:00:18,416
You attend the sermon

6
00:00:19,291 --> 00:00:21,083
And their sermons were...

7
00:00:21,958 --> 00:00:26,375
They didn’t advise people to pray, it was all incitement to fight

8
00:00:26,791 --> 00:00:28,750
They wanted people to join their ranks

9
00:00:29,333 --> 00:00:34,000
But people were aware and knew that what they brought was wrong

10
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:39,708
And there was no one who took their words about joining or not

11
00:00:40,916 --> 00:00:43,916
This hall wasn’t like this

12
00:00:45,083 --> 00:00:50,333
Here the sheikh stood, their sharia official

13
00:00:50,541 --> 00:00:55,791
And here the judges, and here the prisoners sat in this space

14
00:00:56,125 --> 00:00:57,666
And they delivered the sermon to them

15
00:00:58,250 --> 00:01:01,125
About the beard, about the <i>izar</i>  [long pants], and about prayer

16
00:01:02,208 --> 00:01:03,875
And about smoking, that it’s forbidden

17
00:01:04,708 --> 00:01:06,833
We didn’t know that smoking was forbidden

18
00:01:07,875 --> 00:01:09,625
They said that smoking was forbidden
